02. Ничей
03. Песня о совести
04. Дельфины*
05. Признание
06. Дорога*
07. Воспоминание*
08. Драматический этюд*
09. Печальная баллада*

I very like YS' production although he have made not so many groovers but there is some. The most impressive tracks are highlighted above. The most of the most ones are uploaded below — these played by Czech Radio & TV Orchestra and conducted by YS himself.

[yury saulsky - doroga 1977.mp3]   (a real orchestra groove)

[yury saulsky - dramatic etude 1977.mp3]  (there is more of jazz in it)

